User Stories:

Story #1: I want to be able to read job info or rumors on the Web site.

Story #2: I want to be able to read this on a variety of devices, such as desktop and my mobile phone.

Story #3: I want to be able to add my own job info and gossip that I heard about who is hiring.

Story #4: I want to be able to comment on other people's posts.

Story #5: I want to be able to log in and see all my posts and comments.
